\pard\sa80{\cf3\b\fs24 THE FORMAT}\par
\pard\sa180\fs20 Six participants each draft six national teams before the tournament. The 2026 World Cup features 48 teams in 12 groups of four; the top two of each group plus the eight best third-placed teams advance to the Round of 32. You score points for your teams all tournament long \'97 your total is the sum of points earned by your six teams.\par
